{"tid":1862652,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"請求聯合國派出醫療船到港？","createTime":"2020-02-04T17:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T19:13:19.000Z","uid":91967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a08fed7c0d89a07f261303165ce5c9f6def36b3b","tid":1862652,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:46:31.000Z","msg":"《醫護們，你們沒有復工的資格》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1862570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1862570</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完呢個post，發覺根本連設備都冇。<br />\n<br />\n依加根本係叫班揸菜刀既士兵去打有現代化裝備既美軍。<br />\n<br />\n有救人既熱心，但其實背後係非理性既送死！<br />\n<br />\n依家就算肯去添置設備，黎到香港都可能都係半年後既事，到時香港都死咗好多人！<br />\n<br />\n仲未計而加醫院本身就爆哂，普通病房都冇啦，仲點去增加隔離病房？<br />\n<br />\n根本而加唯一出路係外國既支援。"},{"pid":"8d413120d11a6e54ee12e5a6f15741685de5cbab","tid":1862652,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:46:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6727155d4b76a377b49c5e1b709dbcd7cc454b06","tid":1862652,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:47:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f79b55826ceef6237e4b652207b6224758391a1","tid":1862652,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:47:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82d1e5d8dd167f791edb37df26e315276b3144f9","tid":1862652,"uid":249979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:55:33.000Z","msg":"un同世衛都係奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01846abf430d36c0004099196c5e6058e7b7633","tid":1862652,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T18:33:31.000Z","msg":"唔好咁肉酸啦<br />\n香港都要求醫療船，非洲嗰啲點？"},{"pid":"fd8b5f8f59db41f52d01f4ce92e34b9f80d0ff54","tid":1862652,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T18:34:08.000Z","msg":"睇到聯合國三個字已經冇可能"},{"pid":"a3eb6d2a38dd7647bc0668a5a6cefc41f75aaea3","tid":1862652,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82d1e5d8dd167f791edb37